## Description {#details}

The analysis pass which yields a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/phivalues">PhiValues</a>.

The analysis does nothing by itself, and just returns an empty <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/phivalues">PhiValues</a> which will get filled in as it&#39;s used.
